1
00:00:18,251 --> 00:00:19,651
You're always calling me heartless.

2
00:00:20,220 --> 00:00:21,821
But you're the heartless one.

3
00:00:22,522 --> 00:00:23,256
You get a new phone

4
00:00:23,257 --> 00:00:24,924
and tell the whole world to add you.

5
00:00:25,291 --> 00:00:26,411
If I'm the only one missing,

6
00:00:26,826 --> 00:00:27,827
does it even matter?

7
00:00:42,175 --> 00:00:44,244
I'm just one of many contacts to you,

8
00:00:44,778 --> 00:00:46,246
but you're the only one I have.

9
00:00:48,948 --> 00:00:50,517
That's the difference, I guess.

10
00:01:16,876 --> 00:01:17,876
Cut!

11
00:01:18,311 --> 00:01:20,346
Great. Good job.

12
00:01:25,552 --> 00:01:26,652
Maybe it's for the best.

13
00:01:26,653 --> 00:01:28,655
You were born to be this oblivious,

14
00:01:28,855 --> 00:01:31,024
never tied down or overthinking things.

15
00:01:32,091 --> 00:01:33,811
It's enough that I'm the one who remembers.

16
00:01:36,930 --> 00:01:38,665
I only got into this industry

17
00:01:39,199 --> 00:01:40,433
to be closer to you.

18
00:01:41,434 --> 00:01:42,594
I'll treat this collaboration

19
00:01:44,771 --> 00:01:46,840
as a parting gift to myself.

20
00:01:47,674 --> 00:01:50,310
Your most loyal fan in the world

21
00:01:51,177 --> 00:01:52,177
is me.
